metadata.name: bright day in the big city
metadata.description: The drawing depicts a beautiful summer day with a small sailing yacht passing by a bustling city. The sun in the sky is drawn in a way that highlights its heat and size, adding to the overall warm and bright atmosphere of the scene. The use of light and color creates a sense of excitement and freedom, suggesting that the sailing yacht is on an adventure and exploring new places. The city in the background adds a touch of urban life and serves as a contrast to the calmness of the water and the sailboat. Overall, the drawing is aesthetically pleasing and conveys a sense of summertime excitement.
